        <Parent_String>fliers (printed matter) [300224742], declaratory and advertising artifacts [300220524], information artifacts by function [300137961], information artifacts [300230425], information forms (objects) [300220751], Information Forms (hierarchy name) [300026029], Visual and Verbal Communication (hierarchy name) [300264552], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
